          <p> <strong>Short Service (Cessation) / Early Pension</strong> •    If age is above 50 years < less than 58 years
            •   and has completed 10 to 20 years of service.</p>
          <p> <strong>Family Pension if member died while in service</strong> •   Provided he has put in at least 1 month service
            •   If nominated his/her spouse for Family Pension while alive.</p>
          <p> <strong>Family Pension if member died while away from Service ( not in service)</strong> •  If there is no family member,- neither Father nor Mother nor wife nor children
            •   Member can nominate a person while in service.</p>
          <p> <strong>Parent Pension</strong>         •   If no family member neither wife nor children are there.
            •   If there is no Nomination , Parent Pension is admissible to  one of the Dependent Parent if alive</p>
